Make the classes from sun_jce provider get loaded earlier even before your custom class loaders scope. Use those configuration to make your custom class loader delegate the class loading of sun_jce jars to ExtClassLoader. For example : By using Eclipse-BuddyPolicy: ext  in the META-INF of eclipse plugin projects.

